'''''Pride of the Rim''''' was a ship in the [[Corellian Resistance/Legends|Corellian Resistance]] and the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] that got into trouble with an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] picket ship and had to be aided by the [[Retribution (Marauder-class)|''Retribution'']], which in turn was damaged.

